      "path": "audio/narrations/dice-probability/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "拿起一颗骰子，抛出去，会得到 1 到 6 中的某一个点数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dice-probability",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dice-probability/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33840,
      "text": "每一面朝上的机会都一样，这背后藏着概率最古老的思想。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dice-probability",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dice-probability/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "今天我们就从掷骰子出发，看看概率是怎么被算出来的。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dice-probability",
      "section_id": "classical",
      "line_id": "cls-1",
      "filename": "classical-cls-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dice-probability/xiaoxiao/classical-cls-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "骰子的六个面完全对称，出现每个点数的可能性都相等。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dice-probability",
      "section_id": "classical",
      "line_id": "cls-2",
      "filename": "classical-cls-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dice-probability/xiaoxiao/classical-cls-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.48,
      "size": 39600,
      "text": "古典概率说：某事件的概率，等于有利结果数除以等可能结果的总数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dice-probability",
      "section_id": "classical",
      "line_id": "cls-3",
      "filename": "classical-cls-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dice-probability/xiaoxiao/classical-cls-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.48,
      "size": 23616,
      "text": "所以掷出 3 点的概率，就是六分之一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dice-probability",
      "section_id": "distribution",
      "line_id": "dist-1",
      "filename": "distribution-dist-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dice-probability/xiaoxiao/distribution-dist-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "换成两颗骰子，我们关心的是两个点数之和。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dice-probability",
      "section_id": "distribution",
      "line_id": "dist-2",
      "filename": "distribution-dist-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dice-probability/xiaoxiao/distribution-dist-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.15,
      "size": 34416,
      "text": "和为 2 只有一种组合，和为 12 也只有一种，都很稀少。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dice-probability",
      "section_id": "distribution",
      "line_id": "dist-3",
      "filename": "distribution-dist-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dice-probability/xiaoxiao/distribution-dist-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.19,
      "size": 34992,
      "text": "而和为 7 有六种组合，机会最多，图形正中央高高隆起。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dice-probability",
      "section_id": "law",
      "line_id": "law-1",
      "filename": "law-law-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dice-probability/xiaoxiao/law-law-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "真去投掷时，起初的频率会上下波动，并不精确。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dice-probability",
      "section_id": "law",
      "line_id": "law-2",
      "filename": "law-law-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dice-probability/xiaoxiao/law-law-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "但投掷次数越多，实际频率就越稳稳地贴近理论概率。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dice-probability",
      "section_id": "law",
      "line_id": "law-3",
      "filename": "law-law-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dice-probability/xiaoxiao/law-law-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "这个规律叫大数定律，是频率能估计概率的根本原因。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dice-probability",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dice-probability/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.36,
      "size": 37728,
      "text": "不断加大投掷次数，看橙色频率如何一步步压向蓝色理论柱。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dice-probability",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dice-probability/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.0,
      "size": 31968,
      "text": "再试试增减骰子，观察分布怎样从平坦变成钟形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dice-probability",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dice-probability/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "古典概率用等可能结果精确算出理论值。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dice-probability",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dice-probability/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.39,
      "size": 22176,
      "text": "大量试验的频率会逼近这个理论概率。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dice-probability",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dice-probability/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
